  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This NC-1 clean package evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors are fully assessed with achieved levels meeting or exceeding required levels. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed and documented. Sensitivity analysis covers turbulence model variant and inlet boundary condition perturbations. Decision: Accepted.",
